<h4><div class="inline"></div></h4>
<pre class="example code prettyprint"><code class="language-bash">curl https://&lt;canvas&gt;/api/v1/courses/&lt;course_id&gt;/analytics/student_summaries \
    -H 'Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;'</code></pre>
